{"title":"天山下（二首）","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山下（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁匠炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮当当，叮当当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜深沉，声音传的远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一架风箱，一座铁砧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁里一朵红牡丹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新垦的荒，新建的点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一炉红火照天山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修锄犁，打?镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂派出这“小车间”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通红的火花四处溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花里望见了好秋天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下锤，阿不都老爹擦把汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风传来，远处又声声响成片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正笑间，扑啦啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊起宿鸟一大片——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬犁拉来双铧犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛驴驮来砍土镘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿热汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的地，白的天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的树，白的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺天盖地的大雪呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封锁了茫茫草原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声马嘶，一声长鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷起了阵阵雪粉白烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看——呼呼风雪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞来了爬犁一串！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那站在最前的是谁呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手抓缰，一手挥鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎风雪，横肩昂首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲开了雪谷冰山？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，连日里奇寒飞雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邻群的母羊正在生产；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这季节，这季节呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能看它们料缺草断！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕什么雪大风紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么路滑道险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着这列爬犁车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把垛垛干草送进圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漠漠雪海，寒风卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬犁车画出一道线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮帽下是红红的脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈，原来是姑娘阿热汗！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}